{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_06_01",
  "title": "成宮すず 1話 きっと驚きますわよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――クリスマス前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On a day before Christmas",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "月ストの単独ライブ……琴乃の誕生日……\nそしてクリスマスパーティー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest's solo live… Kotono-san's birthday…\nand the Christmas party…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "今年のクリスマスは\n楽しいことが目白押しですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This year's Christmas is\nfilled with exciting events!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "随分と嬉しそうだが\nクリスマスがそんなに楽しみなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem quite happy.\nAre you really looking forward to Christmas this much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "当然です！　今もクリスマスライブに向けて\n新曲を作っていますが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Right now‚ I'm working on a new song for\nthe Christmas live but……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで話し合い、曲がどんどん形になっていくのが\n楽しいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We discuss together‚ and the song is gradually\ntaking shape‚ which is enjoyable!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、琴乃に内緒で集まって\n誕生日のサプライズを計画するのも楽しいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ secretly gathering to plan a surprise for\nKotono-san's birthday is also fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスパーティーに向けて\nツリーや飾り付けを準備するのは楽しいですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preparing the tree and decorations\nfor the Christmas party is exciting too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそうで何よりだが、あまり浮かれ過ぎないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's great to see you excited‚ but don't get carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "浮かれてなんかいませんわ\n私はいつだって冷静沈着ですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not getting carried away.\nI'm always composed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "そっちこそ、本音では私達のクリスマスパーティーに\n参加したいのではございませんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren't you the one who secretly wants to\njoin our Christmas party?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないですわね\n特別にパーティーに招待して差し上げても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can't be helped.\nI'll make a special invitation to",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですわ！　せっかくですから\n琴乃の誕生日サプライズを手伝って下さいませ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the party for you… There! Now‚ please help with\nKotonoha's birthday surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズって何をするつもりなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What kind of surprise are you planning?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "まだ決まっていませんが……\nたとえば、フラッシュモブなんてどうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not decided yet… For example‚\nhow about a flash mob?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "フラッシュモブって、周りにいる人が突然踊り出したり\n演奏を始めたりするパフォーマンスのことだよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A flash mob is when people around suddenly start\ndancing or performing‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "そうです！　ライブ会場へ向かう途中、路上でいきなり\n{user}さんが踊り出すのです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! On the way to the live venue‚ suddenly‚\n{user}-san starts dancing on the street! And then‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "そこに月ストのメンバーも加わって\n琴乃を取り囲んで歌い踊って誕生日を祝うのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest members join‚ surrounding Kotono-san‚\nsinging and dancing to celebrate her birthday!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "きっと琴乃は驚きますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-san will surely be surprised!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "すず、相当浮かれてるな……もうレッスンの時間だろ\nスタジオに移動した方がいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ you're really excited… It's time for our lesson.\nShouldn't we move to the studio?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンより、今はサプライズの話の続きです！\n他にもこういうのはどうかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surprise plan is more important than the lesson right now!\nHow about something like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃が楽屋に入ると\nそこには巨大なプレゼント箱が置いてあって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Kotono-san enters the dressing room‚\nthere's a giant gift box waiting for her――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 129.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "――という感じで、箱の中からサンタコスの\n{user}さんが飛び出すのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Like this‚ {user}-san in a Santa costume\njumps out of the box!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（レッスンしながらサプライズを考えていたのか！）\n（浮かれ過ぎだ。少しは頭を冷やしてもらわないと……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She was planning a surprise while practicing!）\n（She's too excited. She needs to cool down a bit…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "すず、年末は楽しいことばかりじゃないだろ\n期末テストの勉強はしているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ the end of the year isn't all fun.\nAre you studying for your finals?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "期末テスト！　そうでした……\nああ……テスト勉強するのも今から楽しみです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Final exams! Oh‚ right…\nAh‚ studying for exams from now on is also exciting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "テスト勉強が楽しみって、どういうことだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean studying for exams is exciting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "今度、月ストのみんなで沙季の部屋に集まって\nテスト勉強をするんですの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Next time‚ all of Moon Tempest will get together in\nSaki's room to study for the exams.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "みんなでお喋りしたり、おやつを食べたりしながら\n一緒に勉強するなんて、絶対楽しいに決まってますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll chat‚ get some snacks‚ and study together.\nStudying together like that will definitely be fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "テスト勉強まで楽しいなんて\n今年のクリスマスは格別なのですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Studying for exams can be enjoyable too……\nThis Christmas is extraordinary!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "浮かれてるな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem really excited…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに私、学校の成績は優秀ですのよ\n才色兼備とは私のことを言うのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I have excellent grades at school.\nThey say \"talented and beautiful\" to describe me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz023.m4a",
      "text": "この間も芽衣が宿題で悩んでいたので\n勉強を見て差し上げて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Last time‚\nI helped Mei-chan with her homework",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz024.m4a",
      "text": "――そうしたら、芽衣に「すずにゃん頭いい～」と\n褒められたのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――So‚ then Megumi said‚\n\"Suzu-nyan‚ you're so smart!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 205.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz025.m4a",
      "text": "それを見ていた琴乃が「中学生に勉強を教わるって\nどうなの？」と呆れて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's when Kotono‚ who was watching‚ said‚\n\"What's up with getting tutored by middle schoolers ?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（まいったな、もうすぐ出番なのに）\n（話が尽きる気配がないぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Geez‚ Suzu‚ we're about to go on stage soon…）\n（She just keeps talking‚ doesn't she?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すずがクリスマスを楽しみにしているのは分かった\nでも、なぜそこまで楽しみなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ I understand you're looking forward to Christmas‚\nbut why are you so excited?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 227.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz026.m4a",
      "text": "それは……私がこういうクリスマスの過ごし方に\n憧れていたからですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you see‚ I've always admired spending\nChristmas this way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 236.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz027.m4a",
      "text": "成宮家では、クリスマスは大きなツリーを飾って\n家族とごちそうを食べるのが慣例でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the Naramiya household‚ it was customary to decorate a big tree\nand have a feast with family.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz028.m4a",
      "text": "つまり、私は東京に出るまでクリスマスを\n友人達と過ごしたことがなかったのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In other words‚ I had never spent Christmas\nwith friends before I came to Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 247.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 251.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz029.m4a",
      "text": "家族と過ごすクリスマスが嫌な訳ではありませんが\nたまには友達と楽しんでみたいと思っていて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that I dislike spending Christmas with my family‚\nbut I wanted to try having fun with friends for a change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "友達と楽しく過ごすクリスマスは\nすずの憧れだったのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ spending Christmas joyfully with friends was\nyour dream…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 261.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 263.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz030.m4a",
      "text": "ですから、今年のクリスマスは本当に楽しみなのです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! So‚ this Christmas‚ I'm really looking forward to it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 268.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz031.m4a",
      "text": "新曲作りも、勉強会も、パーティーも……\nクリスマスはみんなとずっと一緒で嬉しいのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Creating a new song‚ studying together‚ and having a party…\nChristmas is special because I'll be with everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 272.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 277.1333333333
    },
    {
