      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz032.m4a",
      "text": "……もちろん、『みんな』の中には\n{user}さんも入っていますわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And of course‚ when I say \"everyone‚\"\nI include {user}-san too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 281.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_01-suz033.m4a",
      "text": "という訳で、クリスマスをもっと楽しむために\nお仕事が終わったら次に行きますわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why‚ after we finish work‚\nI'm going somewhere with you to enjoy Christmas even more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
