      "text": "クリスマスムード一色の街を二人で歩いて\nツリーを眺めて、クリスマス気分を高めるのですわ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll walk through the city with full Christmas mood‚\nenjoying the Christmas atmosphere and the tree together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 305.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
